& [ReviewedNarrativeAppendE2EFixtureDesign] is the design contract for isolated reviewed narrative append workflow proof
  @ [created_at] 2026-05-30T08:04:00Z
  @ [append_cli] scripts/narrative-append.ps1
  @ [coverage_cli] scripts/narrative-coverage.ps1
  @ [test_file] tests/test_core.py

  + [design_status] is ready_for_implementation_slice
  + [authority_boundary] is fixture_not_live_project_narrative_mutation
  + [primary_goal] is prove the reviewed narrative append workflow end-to-end inside a temporary project root
  + [non_goal] is writing to coordination/project_narrative_surface.sop in the live workspace
  + [non_goal] is proving semantic truth of the appended narrative
  + [non_goal] is replacing live Manager or Shaliach deliberation
  + [non_goal] is advancing the active conversation frontier

& [FixtureInputs] is the minimal temporary project root
  + [required_file] is coordination/project_narrative_surface.sop
  + [required_file] is coordination/narrative_stale_check.sop
  + [required_file] is coordination/narrative_coverage_update_record.sop
  + [required_file] is coordination/manager_narrative_append_approval.sop
  + [required_file] is coordination/shaliach_narrative_append_clearance.sop
  + [authority_boundary] is temp_fixture_inputs_not_live_surfaces
  = must: create all files under a temporary directory
  = must: keep the live project root out of fixture writes
  = must: use current parser and CLI helper paths rather than duplicating workflow logic

& [FixtureWorkflow] is the expected sequence
  + [step] is write seed project_narrative_surface.sop
  + [step] is write or compute NarrativeStaleCheckRecord evidence
  + [step] is write NarrativeCoverageUpdateRecord evidence
  + [step] is discover current narrative surface guard
  + [step] is write ManagerNarrativeAppendApproval evidence
  + [step] is write ShaliachNarrativeAppendClearance evidence
  + [step] is write plan-mode NarrativeAppendResult evidence
  + [step] is apply reviewed append under the discovered guard
  + [step] is assert final narrative has appended entry and original prefix is preserved
  + [authority_boundary] is fixture_sequence_not_operator_approval

& [ExpectedArtifacts] is the proof shape
  + [artifact_ref] is coordination/narrative_coverage_update_record.sop
  + [artifact_ref] is coordination/manager_narrative_append_approval.sop
  + [artifact_ref] is coordination/shaliach_narrative_append_clearance.sop
  + [artifact_ref] is coordination/narrative_append_plan.sop
  + [artifact_ref] is coordination/narrative_append_result.sop
  + [artifact_ref] is coordination/project_narrative_surface.sop
  = must: plan result status is ready_for_append
  = must: apply result status is applied
  = must: narrative surface contains NarrativeAppliedUpdate
  = must: no live workspace file is touched

& [ProofExpectations] is the minimum implementation proof for this design
  + [test_case] is fixture completes the reviewed append workflow in a temporary project root
  + [test_case] is fixture plan mode does not mutate the temporary narrative before apply
  + [test_case] is fixture apply mode appends reviewed entry and writes applied result
  + [test_case] is fixture uses guard discovery output as the apply guard
  + [test_case] is live coordination/project_narrative_surface.sop is not opened for writing by fixture

& [ImplementationOrder] is the safe next split
  + [slice_1] is add isolated e2e test using Python CLI main functions
  + [slice_2] is add optional operator guide fixture recipe if the test remains readable
  + [slice_3] is refresh checkpoint and audit after e2e fixture
